<div class="text-wrapper">		<span class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><p>The house was sold in foreclosure after Fore was unable to afford monthly payments that nearly doubled, the result of a high-cost refinancing loan from Countrywide.</p>
</span>

		<span class="field field-name-field-image-credit field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><p>Courtesy of the Fores</p>
